              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "GELI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Ge(Li) detector with total efficiency of 21.8%",
                "and peak efficiency of 4.4% (relative to (3x3 NaI(Tl)",
                "detector)"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Target containing several Cu foils, Al and",
                "polystyrene monitor foils were irradiated by high",
                "energy 12C and proton beams. After irradiation the",
                "target was disassembled and individual foils were",
                "measured by Ge(Li) to determine activity of reaction",
                "products. Several measurements were made at different",
                "time intervals, depending on half-life of the measured",
                "radionuclide."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "RCHEM"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " One target foil was radiochemically purified",
                "for the assay of 64Cu. One foil was melted for the",
                "extraction of gaseous products Ar and hydrogen."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "HISTORY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "date": 20111202,
                "history": "C"
              },
              "free_text": [
